{"tid":1603233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"極重要，改善致命傷","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:15:02.000Z","uid":119720,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"144917fcc96e2efa4fd6047d3c709dfe0a2bdcd8","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"今日慘況大家都見到，但唔好氣餒。<br />\n<br />\n我地最致命既致命傷在於： 冇目標<br />\n<br />\n因為冇目標，好多人其實出到嚟唔知應該做咩，好易比羊群心理影響。<br />\n<br />\n結果做成今日中後段既人前前後後fing嚟fing去，而前面就膠著狀態比哂時間啲狗包圍。<br />\n<br />\n解決方法其實好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n1. 每次遊行都需要有清晰目標，包括意義上同實際行動上<br />\n<br />\n2. 每個人請係出嚟前確認好自己出嚟既目標，同樣包括意義上同實際行動上。<br />\n<br />\n有目標自然會比步驟自己，自然個腦就會識郁識思考，點樣保護自己直至達成目標為止。<br />\n<br />\n從來，達成目標=贏 <br />\n<br />\n冇目標=做啲咩都唔會贏。"},{"pid":"8f9a6db0bdd99695c6e7e7cf1488c14390a462ff","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"144917fcc96e2efa4fd6047d3c709dfe0a2bdcd8","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"今日慘況大家都見到，但唔好氣餒。<br />\n<br />\n我地最致命既致命傷在於： 冇目標<br />\n<br />\n因為冇目標，好多人其實出到嚟唔知應該做咩，好易比羊群心理影響。<br />\n<br />\n結果做成今日中後段既人前前後後fing嚟fing去，而前面就膠著狀態比哂時間啲狗包圍。<br />\n<br />\n解決方法其實好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n1. 每次遊行都需要有清晰目標，包括意義上同實際行動上<br />\n<br />\n2. 每個人請係出嚟前確認好自己出嚟既目標，同樣包括意義上同實際行動上。<br />\n<br />\n有目標自然會比步驟自己，自然個腦就會識郁識思考，點樣保護自己直至達成目標為止。<br />\n<br />\n從來，達成目標=贏 <br />\n<br />\n冇目標=做啲咩都唔會贏。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3369a0d4c59230bad334d19413259c93b13190d7","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"c04dad10fc435ef2dd3c02d60a3e023b582b19a3","tid":1603233,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"屌那星推爆佢"},{"pid":"191e7a88a27b174df43a16eb40db0fca595e6d08","tid":1603233,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69175fe7be0e37dd78e8ce74171583f86cbe8745","tid":1603233,"uid":128972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"Tui <br />\n<br />\nBetween<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎蟲</span></span><br />\n食屎大 個腦裝屎<br />\n叫狗其實侮辱咗啲狗狗"},{"pid":"ea2562b8c6ddf69e2dcfedc5eaff2961ed112e99","tid":1603233,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"認同, 但係如果預先定目標, 好容易比黑警預先防守<br />\n<br />\n但現場先定目標, 效率又低"},{"pid":"f72d3b7722f8f4688657e41edd87208527f85772","tid":1603233,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"死黑警屌你老母"},{"pid":"338ccb7b8ae1fe0184df3b20811d82c0ad64bfdc","tid":1603233,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"50d28b9111330005a193883a50c4bc25e57c8cd4","tid":1603233,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c20dedf22090a85a574d9a10c991123ef95600","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea2562b8c6ddf69e2dcfedc5eaff2961ed112e99","tid":1603233,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"認同, 但係如果預先定目標, 好容易比黑警預先防守<br />\n<br />\n但現場先定目標, 效率又低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"所以遊行需要有一個大方向<br />\n<br />\n然後每個人都諗下自己可以為呢個方向去到幾盡/做到啲咩（實際行動）<br />\n<br />\n可以既話，私底下組隊<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，係要建基於同方向同目標之上。"},{"pid":"c98b470cb3ef66e0903e61ca05d498aa740c5da5","tid":1603233,"uid":95259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"tuituitui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> go with the goal."},{"pid":"98b08a4e5739f473963d5bc42e1a6e234a25496f","tid":1603233,"uid":220695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n搵到自己嘅角色好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dfea0d9c21d2913245cf5a9563a2acfdd82482","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"大家諗返起，612果日 我哋全世界人既共同目標就係阻止二讀（意義上）同埋癱瘓立法會（實際行動）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果果日我地成功阻止二讀，贏左一仗<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨諗下，冇左立會做目標，仲有啲咩目標"},{"pid":"c9da6823333b75bd51dc4a65e05f92510da3d338","tid":1603233,"uid":41458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"鬼佬記者都教晒你地<br />\n要有戰略目標，做完就散<br />\n成班人仲出嚟鳩Fing"},{"pid":"dda59f99a1297247f3a1911e3ed3aa365b6f19d4","tid":1603233,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"7a05f6e8ace9f6e376b7258bfd167e607de62433","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9da6823333b75bd51dc4a65e05f92510da3d338","tid":1603233,"uid":41458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"鬼佬記者都教晒你地<br />\n要有戰略目標，做完就散<br />\n成班人仲出嚟鳩Fing"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"係，要有戰略目標，從而有戰略部署"},{"pid":"98953acf3d444bfe94950f006ee9263025f95f5b","tid":1603233,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15affbd0b209958b3eb1c34174780cdf22ee24b7","tid":1603233,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8254b9ac2c616fa3a1c1746d4697374641f48687","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15affbd0b209958b3eb1c34174780cdf22ee24b7","tid":1603233,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69175fe7be0e37dd78e8ce74171583f86cbe8745","tid":1603233,"uid":128972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"Tui <br />\n<br />\nBetween<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎蟲</span></span><br />\n食屎大 個腦裝屎<br />\n叫狗其實侮辱咗啲狗狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"我相信 香港人冇一個係廢尻，只係仲未搵到自己既定位同方向"},{"pid":"d891873b771639f361f1bdbc33b345858a3c30ca","tid":1603233,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"三個月喇<br />\n<br />\n由be water，到Hit and run，到而家獅鳥召喚，最後原來都仲停留喺<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>走走走，見人走我就走</strong></span>，後面半gear同和理非嚇到雞飛狗走都唔知咩事，搞到走散哂，前線好易缺人！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n要退眼望前<br />\n不說走走走，試說急步行<br />\n不說跑呀衝緊埋黎，試說一二一二<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，三個月資訊都仲停留喺嗰邊有狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊度嗰邊！防暴便衣定速龍！數量！</strong></span><br />\n咁模糊嘅資訊好難叫大家部署，然後又係一味走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要時地人一句過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不說嗰邊有狗，試說鵝頸橋五十防暴<br />\n不說呢邊有狗，試說海富橋四十速龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有明明好多時我哋人多佢哋人少，係10：1嗰隻<br />\n都係一味叫走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">都冇人獅鳥冇人踢波<br />\n十月一號仲點樣賀佢老母呀，得把口</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不說有狗走呀，試說有冇人踢波</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4bdb7feef88a0cfbc87c0decdd8601ea90870474","tid":1603233,"uid":286771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n今日完全唔知搞緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a154f9df8027034b000671fb74a3f15f65bc56d","tid":1603233,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b31f184865654d04f55e1ae314402a5ed3061f06","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdb7feef88a0cfbc87c0decdd8601ea90870474","tid":1603233,"uid":286771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n今日完全唔知搞緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔好氣餒！我哋係優秀既香港人，優秀在懂得進步。"},{"pid":"adc227525cada16c5d0b809204f299ff503fe12f","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"推，大家諗下10月1有咩目標有咩方向"},{"pid":"12aaff58dc5c74f7c01a672f7068a53bc42ef405","tid":1603233,"uid":220695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d891873b771639f361f1bdbc33b345858a3c30ca","tid":1603233,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"三個月喇<br />\n<br />\n由be water，到Hit and run，到而家獅鳥召喚，最後原來都仲停留喺<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>走走走，見人走我就走</strong></span>，後面半gear同和理非嚇到雞飛狗走都唔知咩事，搞到走散哂，前線好易缺人！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n要退眼望前<br />\n不說走走走，試說急步行<br />\n不說跑呀衝緊埋黎，試說一二一二<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，三個月資訊都仲停留喺嗰邊有狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊度嗰邊！防暴便衣定速龍！數量！</strong></span><br />\n咁模糊嘅資訊好難叫大家部署，然後又係一味走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要時地人一句過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不說嗰邊有狗，試說鵝頸橋五十防暴<br />\n不說呢邊有狗，試說海富橋四十速龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有明明好多時我哋人多佢哋人少，係10：1嗰隻<br />\n都係一味叫走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">都冇人獅鳥冇人踢波<br />\n十月一號仲點樣賀佢老母呀，得把口</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不說有狗走呀，試說有冇人踢波</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e908494c507f9ff77276f198cadf240be23b2104","tid":1603233,"uid":119720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"因為冇目標，手足比人拉又冇野達成到，所以會覺得唔抵，覺得可惜，覺得心痛，覺得對唔住被捕人。<br />\n<br />\n但如果有目標，達成到，即使比人拉都會冇咁灰。<br />\n<br />\n而比人拉既手足都會覺得自己既犧牲係值得。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有目標唔一定得，但冇目標一定唔得。"},{"pid":"5f72b111f9bd5e3cced5a1f77b2de0c4a5f9f503","tid":1603233,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"十月一全民攝衫"},{"pid":"78ceb03b33d94f5aa0264415d33e53b4559e3f64","tid":1603233,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>在夏慤道撤退後金鐘道的市民也要撤退回灣仔，否則側翼很容易被包抄</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9e7c27a7baade212ff84d48b34f28d351fda36bc","tid":1603233,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"3404a6f53412b75ce5833b847a85424a35a648ef","tid":1603233,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好掛住自high"},{"pid":"305d57bd41f32f882a84629e51c14c6d66f5f6c4","tid":1603233,"uid":168960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"20e0e00b5b44c4b723e4815f89859aa834160631","tid":1603233,"uid":168960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"43f321a9adf2cc89373887d42feb783c5116fbed